================================================================================

LIMITATIONS
================================================================================

Users should be aware of the following limitations:

- Model performance depends on image quality and resolution
- System is trained on specific datasets; generalization may vary
- Batch processing may be memory-intensive for large datasets
- GPU availability recommended for optimal performance
- Models should be regularly retrained with new data
- No real-time inference guarantees

